    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――オーディションから数日後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "オーディション合格おめでとう、千紗\n無事に受かって本当に良かったな",
      "startTime": 5.1955170333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。{user}さんや\n協力してくれたみなさんのおかげです",
      "startTime": 10.9982124762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、まさかあの役に受かっちゃうとは\n思ってもみなかったです",
      "startTime": 18.6666665792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。俺も予想外だったよ\nまさか、よりにもよってあの役に……",
      "startTime": 24.4666666269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "――すみれちゃんに意地悪をする\n悪い子の役になっちゃうなんて……！",
      "startTime": 30.8333332459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "正確には『表向きはいい子だけど、すみれが演じる\nヒロインに裏で意地悪をする、同期の給仕役』だな",
      "startTime": 37.8999999125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "どんな役でも頑張るつもりでいるんです\nでも、誰かに意地悪する役だなんて……",
      "startTime": 46.0333332459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "監督さんからも、本番までにもう少し、役に演技を\n近づけてもらえると嬉しい、って言われましたし",
      "startTime": 55.2666665792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は演技の端々に、どうしても性格の良さが\n出てしまうようだな",
      "startTime": 62.3999991496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗の素が出ないように演技を調整する、か……\nどうすればいいんだろうな",
      "startTime": 69.0666561524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "でも役をいただいたからには全力で頑張ろうと思います\n苦手なことでも、逃げずに向き合っていかないと……",
      "startTime": 76.8999894857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ一度、実際に演じてみてくれないか？\nどれだけ近づける必要があるかを見ておきたい",
      "startTime": 84.9999894857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。えっと、では、お皿を運んでいる\nところで、足を引っかけるシーンを……こほん",
      "startTime": 92.933322819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "あーら、ごめんあそばせ！　足を引っかけて\nしまったかしら？　私、足が長いもので",
      "startTime": 102.0333269357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あらあら。服が汚れてしまっているわよ？\n旦那様の大事なお皿も、大変な、ことに……うぅっ！",
      "startTime": 111.5333279053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうして泣いているんだ、千紗！？\nちゃんとセリフは読めていたぞ！？",
      "startTime": 121.0333279053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません。意地悪されて悲しむ\nすみれちゃんの姿が浮かんできちゃって……",
      "startTime": 127.8666612386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "何も悪いことなんてしてないのに……\nどうしてこんな目に……ふえぇ……",
      "startTime": 134.3666612386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ヒロインをそんな目に遭わせるのが\n千紗が今回演じる役なんだが……",
      "startTime": 140.7999945719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "だが、それと同じ要領で、自分が演じる役に\n感情移入出来れば、いい演技になるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 147.5666632731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかもしれません。でも、意地悪な子に\n感情移入するにはどうしたらいいんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 156.3333299398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺もいい案はまだ浮かんでいないが……\n協力するから、一緒に役作りを頑張ってみよう！",
      "startTime": 163.8999966065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　世界一性格の悪い女の子になれるように\n頑張って特訓します……！",
      "startTime": 172.5333299398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 175.2660736244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！　迎えに来るのが遅いんじゃないですか！？\nこのポンコツマネージャー！",
      "startTime": 181.3999925851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗？　どうしたんだいきなり？\n何か悪い物でも食べたのか……？",
      "startTime": 186.5999762614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、す、すみません！？　これは演技のために\n自分に役を降ろす練習をしているところだったんです",
      "startTime": 193.1999762614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "前に渚ちゃんから、台本を読み込んでいる内に\n役が自分に降りてくることがある、って聞いて",
      "startTime": 201.1999806722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はいくら読んでもうまく降りて来なくって……\nなので、自分から迎えに行くことにしたんです！",
      "startTime": 211.1333095948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これも役作りなのか。なら俺も全力で付き合うぞ！\nさぁ、遠慮はいらない。思い切り罵倒するんだ！",
      "startTime": 220.5666429281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "言われなくてもそうするつもりです！\n察しが悪いですね、この愚図マネージャー！",
      "startTime": 228.3574752323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……ようやくお仕事が終わりました……\nあ、終わったわね。ずっと話していたから喉が渇いたわ",
      "startTime": 239.0666388591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
